NAME
	position-table (display) - read every file in a positions directory as a one-line record and render a scrollable four-column table

INTERFACE
	display (MatrixDisplay)

READS
	positions/		directory listing; every entry attempted
	positions/<name>	single line, whitespace fields:
				asset quantity avg_cost realized_pnl

WRITES
	none (renders only)

DESCRIPTION
	Columns Ticker/Qty/Avg Cost/Real P&L.  The P&L column colours by
	sign of the string; cost and P&L are $-prefixed.  Wheel scrolls
	one row; click or drag in the right gutter jumps the scrollbar
	proportionally.  Re-reads the directory on every update tick.
	The record format is plain whitespace text, not JSON.
